
UNDERSCORE(2)              silmul_efun              UNDERSCORE(2)

名称
     underscore - 把字串加上底线

语法
     string underscore (string str);

描述
     If  this_player()  has  the  "vt100"  attribute  set,   this
     simul_efun  will  return str with the "underscore on" escape
     sequence added in front  and  the  "underscore  off"  escape
     sequence added to the end, so that the string will print out
     in underscore mode on a VT100-compatible terminal.

     注意:  Do NOT use ed to edit the file vt100.c, or the escape
     sequences  will be corrupted.  (ed strips out escape charac-
     ters).

其它参考函数
     inverse, blink,  bold,  clear_screen,  clear_line,  up_line,
     erase_line

作者
     Ichabod@TMI, 3/19/93
     wade@future 4/8/1996 翻译

MudOS Release 0.9         Last change:                   3-19-93

